<L>__{interior cox townhouse bottom of stairs day}
<A>__{he stops at the bottom of the steps, panting. he looks back up the steps, trying to control his heavy breathing so that he can listen. a long silence.}
<C>__{harry}
<D>__{... hello?}
<A>__{no answer. he looks around.}
<L>__{interior cox townhouse kitchen day}
<A>__{harry enters. he opens a drawer, closes it, opens another.}
<L>__{interior cox townhouse foyer day}
<A>__{harry enters from the kitchen and starts slowly mounting the stairs, a chopping knife in one hand.}
<C>__{harry}
<D>__{... hello?}
<L>__{interior cox townhouse second floor day}
<A>__{harry tops the stairs. he pauses, looking at: the bedroom door, ajar. inside, his gun lies on the floor. harry takes cautious steps toward the door. he pauses at the cracked door. suddenly:}
<C>__{harry}
<D>__{hungh!}
<A>__{he plunges through the door and runs for the gun and scoops it, dropping the knife. he stands and spins, panting. his point of view: the closet. its door ajar. legs protrude into the room as if chad, hidden within, is sitting with his back against the closet wall contemplating his next move. harry walks cautiously over. with a bare foot he experimentally waggles one of chad's feet. limp. harry nudges the door.}
<C>__{harry }
<D>__{... hello?}
<A>__{it creaks fully open.}
<C>__{harry }
<D>__{... omygod. omygod.}
<A>__{chad's face is a powder burned, chewed up mess.}
<C>__{harry }
<D>__{... omygod who are you. you fucker. omygod.}
<A>__{he gingerly crouches down.}
<C>__{harry }
<D>__{... you fucker...}
<A>__{he tries to avert his eyes as he feels in chad's suit pockets.}
<C>__{harry }
<D>__{... omygod, my god... ungh...}
<A>__{he comes away with a wallet and hastily stands.}
<C>__{harry }
<D>__{... omygod...}
<A>__{inside are a few dollars and nothing else: no credit cards, driver's license; empty.}
<C>__{harry }
<D>__{... what the fuck...}
<A>__{he leans back in, trying not to look, but for some reason feeling obliged to return the wallet. as he opens the suit coat to slip it back in the inside pocket he notices: the suit label has been cut away. he fingers the raveled fringe.}
<C>__{harry }
<D>__{... oh my fuck...}
<A>__{he straightens up again.}
<C>__{harry }
<D>__{... i killed a fucking spook. you fucker...}
<A>__{he gazes down at the body.}
